J: box invis
   [ folder ] with .c at J.c
   "\f(CWprog2\fP" ljust at J.e

   line from J.s then down boxht/2 then right boxwid/2
K: box invis
   [ document ] with .c at K.c
   "\f(CWsrc1.c\fP" ljust at K.e

   line from J.s then down 3*boxht/2 then right boxwid/2
L: box invis
   [ document ] with .c at L.c
   "\f(CWsrc2.c\fP" ljust at L.e

   line from J.s then down 5*boxht/2 then right boxwid/2
M: box invis
